channel.title: [RESOLVED] Doors Will Not Open [DELTA]
channel.description:
Hey guys, I have recently been having this issue on my RSPS where if I try to open a door, it will just not open, or it will open in a weird direction... I know it is all in the "Doors.cfg" file, and I know how to add a new door and stuff... All of that makes since to me but if I play around with it's code it will still never open. I have tried google'ing it multiple times, and it still does not work.
Any help would be greatly appreciated. Thanks,
Ian1045 :D
